abstracts.cdata!:
The project is being executed by the
            Highway Department in the Ministry of Public Works. The
            final designs and contract documents have been prepared by
            engineering consultants. Consultants will also continue to
            supervise construction. The Highway Department is well
            qualified and with the help of consultants should be able to
            complete the project satisfactorily. The project consists of
            the improvement, construction or reconstruction of seven
            trunk roads, two to upgraded standards, and four feeder roads.
